    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining cornflour</strong> with 50ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[75ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>in the reserved bowl and mix until well combined</p><p>Add 2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>with your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and<strong> tamarind paste</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>ketjap manis </strong>and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong> lime[s] </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Give everything a good mix up until well combined – this is your <strong>pad Thai sauce</strong></p>",
