    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s] </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Once the tofu is crispy, transfer the <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>tofu</strong> to a plate and return the pan to a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped pepper </strong>to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 5-6 min or until the pepper is tender</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1723800133353-x200.jpg",
