            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pepper is cooking, add your <strong>rice noodles</strong> to a pot and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked with a slight bite, drain the <strong>noodles</strong> and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
