    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pepper is tender, reduce the heat to medium</p><p>Push the <strong>pepper </strong>to one side of the pan and crack your <strong>egg[s] </strong>into the other side</p><p>Stir the <strong>egg[s]</strong> with a wooden spoon to break the yolk[s] and cook for 1-2 min until it resembles scrambled egg, then mix it all through the pepper</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
