          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>pad Thai sauce</strong> to the pan with the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and<strong> chopped spring onion</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>cooked noodles </strong>and<strong> crispy tofu</strong></p><p>Cook for a final 1 min and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>crispy tofu pad Thai</strong></p>",
